  <CalDefinition Description="If lockout behavior is triggered, the user is prohibited from accessing the Trailer Length Overlay screen if the user has not created any trailer profiles. If user is already on the Trailer Length Overlay screen or in the Profile Wizard flow, the view will change back to the top level Settings view. " Name="TrailerLengthOverlayDriverWorkload" References="GIS-539 5.5.1.2*MY20 Driver Workload Restriction Items" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
