  </CalDefinition>
  <CalDefinition Description="If lockout behavior is triggered, the user is prohibited from acessing the Enter Trailer Length screen, either by pressing the toggle when no lengths have been entered or by pressing on any list items on the Trailer Length Overlay screen. If user is al&#xac;ready in the Enter Trailer Length view, the view will change back to the Trailer Length Overlay Setting view. " Name="TrailerLengthOverlaySettingDriverWorkload" References="GIS-539 5.5.1.2*MY20 Driver Workload Restriction Items" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
