  <CalDefinition Description="This calibration turns the Trailering App app on or off on the home screen for light or heavy duty truck in North American Region. This cal is used to determine trailering functionality available on the vehicle. If set to 0, trailer app is disabled. If set to 1, trailer app contains Trailer Light Sequence functionality only. Option selected when Trailering Interface Module is NOT packaged on the vehicle (RPO U1D is NOT packaged). If set to 2, trailer app contains full Trailering Features. Option selected when Trailering Interface Module is packaged on the vehicle (RPO U1D is packaged) " Name="TraileringAppType" References="GIS-539 &amp; GIS-739" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
    <CalID>_1ucVoHKvEeWtPcYjqrxpUw</CalID>
    <Type>Enumeration</Type>
