      <Description>Updated the usage field for this calibration to support the new &quot;Global A/B&quot; categorization in the CalDef tool.</Description>
      <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
    <CalDefChangeRecord>
      <Version>4</Version>
      <Date>9/26/2017</Date>
      <Description>Updated vehicle architectural usage to add GEM usage for this calibration because it fell within the current criteria of calibrations that require GEM usage, which are any calibrations that would be used for Low Radio Global B application.</Description>
      <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
